
-- The data file needs to be terminated with a
-1 -1
on the very last line.  This makes reading the file a whole lot easier
to handle.


-- Keys for Camera movement
  
 q w  dec/inc X eye point coord
 a s  dec/inc Y eye point coord
 z x  dec/inc Z eye point coord
 e r  dec/inc X camera point coord
 d f  dec/inc Y camera point coord
 c v  dec/inc Z camera point coord
  

-- Entire camera code can be disabled by commenting out 
//define CAMERA
  at the beginning of OGLRen.h
